title: Guitar Pro v1.5.3
description:
This mobile version of the famous Guitar Pro tab-editing program is the ideal companion for you to practice your favorite songs and share them at any time, anywhere!

An arpeggio, a riff, a chord sequence ringing in your head? You can now note and save all this on the tablature notepad available with the iPhone update.
